{"tid":1350111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚咁少上環post其實唔緊要","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:09:41.000Z","uid":123647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cebb149f06c7ca63752988428c168be937403edf","tid":1350111,"uid":123647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔係話上環條戰線唔洗理、亦唔係唔洗理上環手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔緊要既原因係其實尋晚係試水溫<br />\n<br />\n搵黑道做嘢好明顯唔係真係要佢地打手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而係要睇下大家對上環既關注度有幾大</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今次佢地試水溫出黎結果係尋晚成個熱門page冇post講上環，同埋記者會大家只係啄住元朗；上環開36槍已經成為小事<br />\n<br />\n我有理由相信收買黑道<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定會再發生</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而下一次既目標都係要分散焦點<br />\n<br />\n今次算係演習，大家見到上環手足關注度遠低於元朗黑幫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>解決方案</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實好簡單，下次有維穩部隊出動既同時，如果<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同一時間都有手足做緊野</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家要風向唔可以只係focus喺同一邊，一定要兩邊、三邊都要有人mon住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人在外國，恕小弟做唔到勇武；只希望喺文宣、mon post幫到手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d093d211660143ee1548e6138d384d4518935148","tid":1350111,"uid":123647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:02:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b07997a2e702cc053100e726d88a8f07c9011b5","tid":1350111,"uid":123647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:02:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0d628f58639f41595da22cf9f043e573d1239ec","tid":1350111,"uid":123647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32a00cb8d854ba22b8679c745aec2ab126723c1","tid":1350111,"uid":123647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:05:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21029fa0d38312c673841cc6f6120508cb9efa56","tid":1350111,"uid":123647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:07:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"965c77c3cd869cf6486026ff28bebbc024735b62","tid":1350111,"uid":123647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}